&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; WPT uses popups extensively to test features that rely on top-level
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; navigation. Navigation timing, render-blocking, cross-document view
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; transitions come to mind as reference.
