&lt;pre&gt;&gt; * Is this just extending existing support on desktop platforms for this
feature to Android?&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

Yes.

&gt; * Are there any API shape changes to support serial over Bluetooth, or is
it handled entirely by the UA?

No changes to any API spec. The UA handles the platform differences.

