&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; - could you describe how this experiment is similar or different (or
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; perhaps builds upon the results from the previous experiment)?
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; thanks,
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Mike
