&lt;pre&gt;Hi Yoav,

For
 &gt;&gt;&quot; Would that change current rendering of sites that don't set any 
accent-color?&quot;
*Yes*, when accent-color is not set, it is basically set to default value 
&quot;auto&quot;, which will take system's accent color with this change.
