&lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/webmachinelearning/translation-api/issues/36"&gt;https://github.com/webmachinelearning/translation-api/issues/36&lt;/a&gt;&gt; to use
this API. I am also sharing our latest OT feedback
&lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/webmachinelearning/meetings/blob/main/telcons/2025-02-26-cg-minutes.md"&gt;https://github.com/webmachinelearning/meetings/blob/main/telcons/2025-02-26-cg-minutes.md&lt;/a&gt;&gt;
