&lt;pre&gt;3 potential sites in the 12 M for something almost certainly
minor/superficial UI breakage indeed seems exceedingly low risk to me.&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

LGTM3 to ship. But as always, if you get reports of breakage prior to
hitting stable, please use the kill-switch and circle back here for a more
thorough compat analysis discussion.

Rick


