&gt;
&gt; *WebKit*: No signal (
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/WebKit/standards-positions/issues/527"&gt;https://github.com/WebKit/standards-positions/issues/527&lt;/a&gt;)
&gt;
&gt; *Web developers*: Positive (
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/8376"&gt;https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/8376&lt;/a&gt;) Positive feedback from
&gt; developers in the original github issue.
&gt;
&gt; *Other signals*:
&gt;
