&gt;&gt; Blink.
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; In general,
&gt;&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://chromium.googlesource.com/chromium/src/+/main/styleguide/c++/c++-features.md"&gt;https://chromium.googlesource.com/chromium/src/+/main/styleguide/c++/c++-features.md&lt;/a&gt;
&gt;&gt; tries to default allow features in older C++ versions, with specific
&gt;&gt; callouts to things that are banned.
&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Daniel
